sub_title: Senior Research Technician at Maastricht University
summary:
Specialties: 
• electrophysiology; patch-clamp (voltage- and current clamp), ion-channels, dynamic clamp
• laboratory techniques: Western blot, cell culture, transfections
• data analysis
• scientific writing
• lab management
• molecular and biochemical lab techniques
• scientific illustrations

• Sharp microelectrode technique: to obtain cardiac action potentials from isolated mammalian cardiac myocytes and from multi-cellular preparations. Data acquisition, analysis and publication in this field.

• Lab manager
• General techniques: cell culturing, transfections, Western blot.
